             was indicted for <rs id="t17950701-20-off107" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17950701-20-off107" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17950701-20-off107" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17950701-20-cd108" type="crimeDate">4th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950701-20-off107 t17950701-20-cd108"></join>, fifty-six yards of rope, value 6s.
            </rs> the goods of <rs id="t17950701-20-viclabel109" type="occupation">Messrs.</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950701-20-victim300 t17950701-20-viclabel109"></join>
